      <title>苏表示美国就业报告显示经济稳步增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/jobs-reports-shows-steady-growth-su-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代理劳工部长 Julie Su 表示，美国 8 月份就业报告显示就业增长强劲且稳定。就业人数增加 142,000 人，低于预期的 165,000 人。前两个月的就业数据也出现下调。Su 在“彭博未平仓合约”节目中发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/jobs-reports-shows-steady-growth-su-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:06:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>规模达 3500 亿美元的基金将受到标普新指数上限规则的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/funds-with-350-billion-are-exposed-to-s-p-s-new-index-cap-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔道琼斯指数公司修改了规则，以遏制大公司的主导地位。本月晚些时候，资产规模达 3500 亿美元的指数跟踪股票基金将进行大规模改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/funds-with-350-billion-are-exposed-to-s-p-s-new-index-cap-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:06:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的里德：市场降息定价“激进”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/blackrock-s-rieder-market-rate-cut-pricing-aggressive-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球固定收益首席投资官里克·里德 (Rick Rieder) 认为，美联储应该在本月晚些时候降息 50 个基点，但他预计美联储将“谨慎”降息 25 个基点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/blackrock-s-rieder-market-rate-cut-pricing-aggressive-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 13:53:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据引发美联储降息幅度争论，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/latest-gold-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业报告好坏参半，加剧了有关美联储 9 月份会议上将如何大幅降息的争论，导致金价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/latest-gold-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 13:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储威廉姆斯称现在适合降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-now-appropriate-to-lower-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行行长约翰威廉姆斯表示，鉴于降低通胀和劳动力市场降温的进展，现在央行降低利率是适当的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-now-appropriate-to-lower-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>央行降息前 AT1 债券销量创下周度新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/at1-bond-sales-hit-weekly-record-ahead-of-central-bank-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自全球金融危机爆发后引入此类高风险银行债务以来，银行正经历最繁忙的一周，发行额外一级债券。]]></description>
