      <title>TGI Friday’s 因文件延迟而失去资产控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/tgi-friday-s-loses-control-of-assets-following-document-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于未能及时向债券持有人提交文件，TGI Friday’s Inc. 管理层失去了对该连锁餐厅大部分资产和职能的日常控制。]]></description>
